data.title: Film Reviews
data.meta_description: New film reviews are written by staff, librarians, teachers, and film critics. These reviews rate the educational value of selected fiction movies.
data.text:
Film is an artistic medium that communicates ideas, stories, perceptions, and feelings through the use of moving images. Here you'll find reviews of films from various genres as well as articles on programming and crafting a well-rounded film collection.
